ygData.messageBody:
Yes,
9:30 PM EDT (we're in daylight time now)
=8:30 PM CDT
=7:30 PM MDT
=6:30 PM PDT

I'll be reading up on all the guild commands tonight before the meeting.
Once again, the channel will be "Unity" and the password will be "rainbow"
in all lower case letters.

See you all then. If we don't get 10 people by 10 PM EDT, then we'll try and
schedule a time over the weekend.
